About Myself

Hello! My name is Juliana, and I live in Ontario, Canada. I am looking for innovation, new opportunities, and challenging projects. My family and to settle in Canada were the most successful plans of my life.

I have been interested in technology since childhood and have accumulated ten years of experience. My background started as a developer for five years, then a systems analyst, and since then I have been leading teams with a passion for well-done results.

At first, I did not imagine to be a leader, but my father was my greatest inspiration source. Moreover, little by little I naturally felt that I appreciate helping and dedicating myself to people.

"Leaders must inspire and motivate to raise new leaders."

Juliana
); }
